\"TI\"], \",\", StyleBox[\"b\", \"TI\"]}], \"]\"}]\) gives a list of the \
numbers of 1, 2, \[Ellipsis], \!\(\*RowBox[{\"b\", \"-\", \"1\"}]\), 0 digits \
